Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我這就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 拿著…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏面有…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你長大以後…要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.98,0:00:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.58,0:00:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 你的命運…托付給高達…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.11,0:01:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1400)}媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又夢見當時的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.46,0:01:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 趕緊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 趕緊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一則新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星運輸船遭不明物體襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20名船員去向不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍緊急應對總部認為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次事件系UE…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即未知敵人的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件仍在調查中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自UE發動的第一起襲擊事件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「天使隕落之日」後14年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦政府至今宣稱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法探明敵人的真實身份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市民的不滿日益高漲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來了嗎 菲利特 菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 又熬夜了對不對？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩眼通紅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布魯扎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午開始的啟動實驗 通知你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然！司令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:04:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是個普通孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的才能讓所有人都驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快 趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動實驗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 高達馬上就能站起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼急…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 沒傷著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 原來是菲利特和艾米莉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…不是高達的手臂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼裝在那上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試看好不好使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到運動性太棒了 不捨得拆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要試用高達部件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得事先通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 高達是司令專門委託給菲利特的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 遲到了 菲利特 遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:05:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 要遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再自作主張了 凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特真是 提起高達就激動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達是特殊的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:52.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺 您請看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是明日野家族世代相傳的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的戰士 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 在過往的大戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它被稱作是為世界帶來和平的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些戰士們 過去也被叫做MOBILE SUIT
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MOBILE SUIT?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 巨大的人形兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MOBILE SUIT
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中的眾多名機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都出自代代經營MS製造業的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明日野家族 少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要製造出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的救世主 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說嗎 外星人又惹事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外星人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是UE嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來歷不明 不是外星人是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:07:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人們都這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 只要住在諾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和我們沒什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們就沒怎麼來過人多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼讓我們開始上課
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先從…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 老師來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師怎麼看昨天的事件？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貨船疑似被UE襲擊的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們 是不是也該想好應對措施？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座諾拉也不是絕對安全的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特的被害妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有危險的話 會發佈警告的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 到現在為止從來沒有過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE的襲擊 有一定規律性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據規律解開方程式…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 答案表明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次遭襲的就是諾拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有完沒完！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想什麼 菲利特？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看你現在成績優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦鬆懈馬上就會落後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為去摻和軍方那個什麼機動戰士開發計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會滿腦子這些不切實際的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當初就反對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到座位上去 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想被退學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 挨罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 挨罵…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人說不定已經在附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離上次來天文館 有多久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我想太多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.78,0:10:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾拉會被襲擊的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座衛星上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只把那些看成是發生在遙遠世界的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為誰都沒有被UE襲擊過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我親眼看見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故鄉奧凡在UE的襲擊中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個城市瞬間化作火海的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們根本殺人不眨眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽臨死前 給我的記憶體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說 這裏面有我該做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏面記錄有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:11:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士的設計圖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前家裏畫像上一模一樣的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是提到的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫中的救世主 對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是那台白色戰士的稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽一定想說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我製造機動戰士去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰鬥中 拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以菲利特造的機動戰士也叫做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是救世主的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 城市裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那閃光是…爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是它們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是UE！ 這樣下去城市就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是UE…他們真的來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人確認為UE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防衛隊請出戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士是什麼情況 出動如此緩慢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外的Genoace直接前往迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三號機庫 德列斯小隊能否出擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們抓緊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去出口會被控制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克 古魯迪克副司令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮防守第四到第八防區
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們會來這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉你不用來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:01.16,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,660)\fs30}（全員戰鬥配置）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:04.02,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,660)\fs30\fad(0,400)}（重複 全員戰鬥配置）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE的攻擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手是外星人 該怎麼打？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 艾米莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Genoace
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在等什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 想急死我這個老頭子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是UE的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是什麼機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們只會到處破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台搬運車上 運的是高達？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 敵人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我趕忙把它藏到這裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏起來？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的Genoace被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯 出動高達
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達可以戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 老爺子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台新型機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.38,0:14:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 高達還動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離實戰差遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試時站起來走了兩步而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣足以確認運動性了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個 拉甘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對第一次駕駛的人來說風險太大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用Genoace出戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 這裏也很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去裏面避難
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你想…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不是駕駛員 怎麼可能開得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我造的高達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體的情況 我最瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是瞭解就能打贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是戰爭！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉甘·德列斯 Genoace出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請趕緊打開艙門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14年來從沒被人擊敗過的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉甘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,營救駕駛員 趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准去！你會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拉甘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 抬他出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 什麼都沒做成…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 大家都會死…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人就是那樣殘暴 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只有戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平衡器只能邊駕駛邊調節了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 老爺子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會是想讓菲利特開它吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特的覺悟是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不輸給大兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用媽媽給我的這台高達
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和它們戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來啟動順利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.59,0:17:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我升起托架了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實不想讓你去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…一直看在眼裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特有多麼認真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特的戰鬥就永遠不會結束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量系統 正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系統 啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你的了 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 高達好像要出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員是拉甘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在上面？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布魯扎先生 這是我的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 一定要活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去救出大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特·明日野 高達出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型機準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四機庫防爆艙門確認開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好幹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們見識見識 你傳說中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥吧 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為大家 也為你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為救世主 與高達一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一台 就這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 有什麼武器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用 那麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.56,0:20:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了嗎 UE的機動戰士型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 高達
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有增援 想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 這就是戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來 還不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特果然是個了不起的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙什麼時候變得這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們勝利了 史上首次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.15,0:21:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這種程度的戰果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會改變任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.23,0:21:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以成為反擊的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.57,0:21:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在好好享受這份勝利…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.23,0:22:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛才的機動戰士型
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是來自衛星外部的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報復嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使隕落之日 又要重演…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.05,0:22:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:24:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故鄉大地被未知敵人的魔爪蹂躪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.73,0:24:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這時 高達發動真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.28,0:24:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.82,0:24:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE之力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.42,0:24:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人的命運成就歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.44,0:24:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達是根據媽媽托付給我的AGE裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.56,0:24:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我們製造出的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.01,0:24:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為和明日野家族畫像上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.47,0:24:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的白色救世主高達非常相似
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.62,0:24:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我給它起名為 高達

